MALACAÑANG MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 552

ESTABLISHING AS MT. MATUTUM PROTECTED LANDSCAPE THE PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED WITHIN THE MUNICIPALITIES OF TUPI, TAMPAKAN, AND POLOMOLOK, PROVINCE OF SOUTH COTABATO, AND THE MUNICIPALITY OF MALUNGON, PROVINCE OF SARANGANI

